{"tid":1941380,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"★麥當勞夜間禁堂食圍封座位　「麥難民」將無法留宿","createTime":"2020-03-24T11:30:55.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-24T12:06:33.000Z","uid":19454,"like":5,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"7f101735c734569a4b9ba209724e36f89da8ee34","tid":1941380,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-24T11:30:55.000Z","msg":"膠帶圍封店內部份位置<br />\n<br />\n麥當勞企業傳訊高級總監林婉梅表示，由於現時的疫情嚴峻，為了職員及顧客的著想，暫停晚更堂食兩星期，並已跟前線同事聯絡作配合上班時間。問到她會如何關閉堂食位時林表示會因應餐廳大小，以膠帶等圍著堂食位置處理，部份分店的範圍較大，將會局部關處理。<br />\n<br />\n麥難民無法留宿 「抱歉未能提供地點」<br />\n<br />\n一向以來，有部份「麥難民」晚上會於餐廳休息，餐廳方面表示由於疫情嚴峻，明白到未來兩星期為「關鍵時間」，亦提早結構每日堂食時間，坦言抱歉未能提供地點作息。「生意始終可以長做有，現時最重要都會擔心顧客同員工安全，之後有人出事做幾多意都補唔返損失，因此生意有所影響作此決定。」<br />\n<br />\n餐廳公布，所有分店於下午6時後不提供堂食，只設外賣及麥麥送服務，包括24小時餐廳，香港麥當勞行政總裁黎韋詩表示，餐廳作為社會一分子，非常關注僱員和廣大市民的健康，會調整營運模式，不鼓勵堂食，只設外賣及麥麥送，希望能做到減少社交接觸，進一步保障僱員及顧客安全，與社會共同抗疫。<br />\n<br />\n餐廳提到，為配合營運新安排，於每日下午6時至午夜12時使用24小時麥麥送訂餐服務，一律免運費，此外，麥當勞企業傳訊高級總監林婉梅表示，由於現時的疫情嚴峻，為了職員及顧客的著想，暫停晚更堂食兩星期，並已跟前線同事聯絡作配合上班時間。問到她會如何關閉堂食位時林表示會因應餐廳大小，以膠帶等圍著堂食位置處理，部份分店的範圍較大，將會局部關處理。<br />\n<br />\n不接待檢疫人士 但可送餐至大堂<br />\n<br />\n此外，因應香港政府早前宣布進一步加強防疫的抗疫措施，麥當勞暫不接待正接受強制檢疫人士，但仍可透過麥麥送享用美食，如外送地址屬於確診或家居隔離人士的住所名單內，外送員會將食物派送至大廈大堂，以達致零接觸取餐。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hk01.com/%E7%A4%BE%E6%9C%83%E6%96%B0%E8%81%9E/452124/%E6%96%B0%E5%86%A0%E8%82%BA%E7%82%8E-%E9%BA%A5%E7%95%B6%E5%8B%9E%E5%A4%9C%E9%96%93%E7%A6%81%E5%A0%82%E9%A3%9F%E5%9C%8D%E5%B0%81%E5%BA%A7%E4%BD%8D-%E9%BA%A5%E9%9B%A3%E6%B0%91-%E5%B0%87%E7%84%A1%E6%B3%95%E7%95%99%E5%AE%BF\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2F%25E7%25A4%25BE%25E6%259C%2583%25E6%2596%25B0%25E8%2581%259E%2F452124%2F%25E6%2596%25B0%25E5%2586%25A0%25E8%2582%25BA%25E7%2582%258E-%25E9%25BA%25A5%25E7%2595%25B6%25E5%258B%259E%25E5%25A4%259C%25E9%2596%2593%25E7%25A6%2581%25E5%25A0%2582%25E9%25A3%259F%25E5%259C%258D%25E5%25B0%2581%25E5%25BA%25A7%25E4%25BD%258D-%25E9%25BA%25A5%25E9%259B%25A3%25E6%25B0%2591-%25E5%25B0%2587%25E7%2584%25A1%25E6%25B3%2595%25E7%2595%2599%25E5%25AE%25BF&d=Afoh3Yf6cz19ESyehd0SJ4TtxWFByFwd8BqLGIwhgUE%3D&h=5af5ca95\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.hk01.com/%E7%A4%BE%E6%9C%83%E6%96%B0%E8%81%9E/452124/%E6%96%B0%E5%86%A0%E8%82%BA%E7%82%8E-%E9%BA%A5%E7%95%B6%E5%8B%9E%E5%A4%9C%E9%96%93%E7%A6%81%E5%A0%82%E9%A3%9F%E5%9C%8D%E5%B0%81%E5%BA%A7%E4%BD%8D-%E9%BA%A5%E9%9B%A3%E6%B0%91-%E5%B0%87%E7%84%A1%E6%B3%95%E7%95%99%E5%AE%BF</a>"},{"pid":"ce214f832eab448ac0c49acbbc37994b41225b9b","tid":1941380,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-24T11:31:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"939d88cc2bd10b6d89c132668c5b6843ba27ba1e","tid":1941380,"uid":275238,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-24T11:32:20.000Z","msg":"麥難民，反抗！"},{"pid":"b8b4ddfa2428c1619dd112e19cae6dd992575c69","tid":1941380,"uid":257974,"like":9,"dislike":2,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-24T11:33:18.000Z","msg":"咁都入m記數?<br />\n善心人唔撚租間屋比佢地訓?"},{"pid":"ca6768ada3a6cc2f974ce290ac900ace4ad5cbd0","tid":1941380,"uid":237562,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-24T11:37:17.000Z","msg":"No more 2nd hand 飯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"be9562d16c5084ffa1994b55213292ee9b1a5d89","tid":1941380,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-24T11:39:24.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">【2020-03-24】4名武漢肺炎患者危殆   醫管局再籲市民如非必要勿外出 </span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<br />\nSOURCE:<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/video-gallery.htm?vid=1516529\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fvideo-gallery.htm%3Fvid%3D1516529&d=Afoh3Yf6cz19ESyehd0SJ4TtxWFByFwd8BqLGIwhgUE%3D&h=bb067087\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fvideo-gallery.htm%3Fvid%3D1516529&h=76562948\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/video-gallery.htm?vid=1516529</a><br />\n<br />\n醫院管理局總行政經理何婉霞說，目前有4名武漢肺炎患者情況危殆，有病人昨日氣促情況惡化，需要插喉使用呼吸機協助呼吸。<br />\n<br />\n她預計未來患者數目將會增加，期望市民配合醫護人員的努力，強調如果入院病人不斷增加，不論醫護人員多努力增開病房及增加人手，始終有日會應付不來，呼籲市民合作，如非必要不要外出，在人多地方盡量縮短逗留時間及戴口罩，認為這是對醫護最大的支持。<br />\n<br />\n何婉霞又說，醫院餐廳將實行特別措施，為訪客及病人只提供外賣，不設堂食，希望減低病人及訪客在餐廳逗留的時間。"},{"pid":"95d4351b29e2e6e6fc25fe04f33c4c91c0639a93","tid":1941380,"uid":121146,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-24T11:41:06.000Z","msg":"乜應份比你訓架咩？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 社區中心黎架？"},{"pid":"ccc2f51c0cdc364ad565b9e82e8c42817137d619","tid":1941380,"uid":89046,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-24T11:41:12.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/hbfxJGEdCEs\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FhbfxJGEdCEs&d=Afoh3Yf6cz19ESyehd0SJ4TtxWFByFwd8BqLGIwhgUE%3D&h=0924254c\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/hbfxJGEdCEs</a><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"56c755daa00c1b37379a721b96d56d64fd10d8b9","tid":1941380,"uid":97904,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-24T11:48:39.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"> hk01 </span></span>"},{"pid":"f5f6949d3a2d92d95dc928879df1c86827138284","tid":1941380,"uid":997,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-24T11:51:17.000Z","msg":"屌你老